description: Submission of reserved matters application (appearance, landscaping, layout and scale) for Plot 1 only, pursuant to condition 15 of parent planning permission ref:19/4398/O dated 21 May 2021 as amended under S73 planning permission ref:21/3540/MA dated 09 November 2022 and S73 planning permission ref: 22/3782/MA dated 17th March 2023 comprising the construction of 328 residential units with associated parking and private and public open spaces.
